\
This application sets the rating for all tracks in your iTunes library according to how often each track is played, and how often each track is skipped.\
\
The formula uses a combination of play and skip frequency (averaged out over the life of each track), and the play and skip count. Tracks that are frequently skipped are penalised, while often-played tracks are given a higher rating.\
\

