\f0\b Default configuration and overriding ratings
\f1\b0 \
\
By default, AutoRate will only rate tracks that you have not rated.  Thus, if you wish to continue using AutoRate to update your ratings, you will need to open AutoRate's preferences and allow AutoRate to override ratings.\
\

